description:
Энэхүү аппликэйшн нь тоон гарын үсгийн гэрчилгээг төрөөс иргэдэд үнэ төлбөргүй олгох, түүнийг ашиглан иргэд цахим орчинд гарын үсгээ зурж, баталгаажуулах үндсэн зорилготой бөгөөд Монгол улсын "Цахим гарын үсгийн тухай" хуульд заасны дагуу зөвхөн 16 буюу түүнээс дээш насны Монгол улсын иргэд ашиглана. 

This application is dedicated to issuing digital signature certificates to citizens of Mongolia free of charge and using them to sign and verify signatures for online services. According to the law of Mongolia on Digital Signatures, it can only be used by citizens of Mongolia who are 16 years of age or older.

Google Authenticator adds an extra layer of security to your online accounts by adding a second step of verification when you sign in. This means that in addition to your password, you'll also need to enter a code that is generated by the Google Authenticator app on your phone.

The verification code can be generated by the Google Authenticator app on your phone, even if you don't have a network or mobile connection.

• Sync your Authenticator codes to your Google Account and across your devices. This way, you can always access them even if you lose your phone.

• Set up your Authenticator accounts automatically with a QR code. This is quick and easy, and it helps to ensure that your codes are set up correctly.

• Support for multiple accounts. You can use the authenticator app to manage multiple accounts, so you don't have to switch between apps every time you need to sign in.

• Support for time-based and counter-based code generation. You can choose the type of code generation that best suits your needs.

• Transfer accounts between devices with a QR code. This is a convenient way to move your accounts to a new device.


To use Google Authenticator with Google, you need to enable 2-Step Verification on your Google Account. To get started, visit http://www.google.com/2step

File sharing has never been simpler! Without the need of a cable or cellular data, you can share files from device to device for free with Zapya. Zapya allows you to seamlessly transfer massive files across multiple platforms with speeds up to 10MB/second or up to 260 pictures in a minute. 

Looking to quickly connect with someone nearby? With the support of GPS location, Zapya provides a fast and accurate way to find nearby devices. You can also shake your devices at the same time in order to connect. Zapya can support USB Backup and Restore on iPad.

Another way to connect on Zapya is via QR Codes. You can generate a personalized QR code in order to share multiple files at once. Others just need to scan the QR code to have the files to instantly start downloading onto their phone. Without touching your keyboard, you can share files to others! 

If you have important files on your device that you do not want others to have access to, you can select and lock those files into a hidden folder. By doing this, the next time you go to share files with someone; they will not be able to see or access those files.  

Besides sharing files, you can chat offline with up to five other devices using Zapya. You can also move the phone log and photos from your old device to your new phone in a matter of minutes. Or if you want to take photos remotely, you can use the PeerCam feature and control the camera of a connected device with peer permission. 

If you like Zapya, please give us reviews and high ratings. Your support is much appreciated!

If you experience any issues or have any suggestions, please send feedback to us within the app or contact: feedback@dewmobile.net.

Disclaimer: This app may use your location even when it is not open, which can decrease device battery life.
